\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6}{\ignorespaces Two-stage training dynamics. Stage\nonbreakingspace 1 (purple): pretraining on 413 multi-asset samples. Stage\nonbreakingspace 2 (teal): fine-tuning on 362 crypto assets (dashed line = init from Stage\nonbreakingspace 1 checkpoint). (a)\nonbreakingspace NLL improves in both stages. (b)\nonbreakingspace Val CRPS drops after crypto fine-tuning. (c)\nonbreakingspace Predicted $\mu $ spread grows in Stage\nonbreakingspace 2. (d)\nonbreakingspace $\nu $ stabilizes near 2. (e)\nonbreakingspace Total loss with resume point. (f)\nonbreakingspace Gradient norm increases during adaptation.}}{7}{figure.caption.30}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:training}{{6}{7}{Two-stage training dynamics. Stage~1 (purple): pretraining on 413 multi-asset samples. Stage~2 (teal): fine-tuning on 362 crypto assets (dashed line = init from Stage~1 checkpoint). (a)~NLL improves in both stages. (b)~Val CRPS drops after crypto fine-tuning. (c)~Predicted $\mu $ spread grows in Stage~2. (d)~$\nu $ stabilizes near 2. (e)~Total loss with resume point. (f)~Gradient norm increases during adaptation}{figure.caption.30}{}}
